[i|## Conclusion|/|tilde.pink|70]
[i||/|tilde.pink|70]
[i|It’s a pretty fun and laid-back project that helps me pass|/|tilde.pink|70]
[i|the time sometimes. The only downside is certain differences|/|tilde.pink|70]
[i|between Python and Nix, such as Nix’s lazy evaluation, which|/|tilde.pink|70]
[i|can make porting to Python complicated.|/|tilde.pink|70]

